---

NOTE: This project uses Stockfish and GNU Chess (both GPLv3) as external
UCI subprocesses via python-chess. python-chess itself is GPLv3. No source
is linked or bundled; communication is via stdin/stdout pipe.

The polyglot opening book `/usr/share/games/gnuchess/book.bin` shipped by
the Debian `gnuchess-book` package is GPL-licensed; `chess-tui` reads it
at runtime but does not redistribute it.

The puzzle dataset sample (`data/puzzles_sample.csv`) derives from
Lichess's public puzzle database which is published CC0.
